{
  "chapter": 265,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙回到听松别馆，池子春谎称发现董淑贞与沙立幽会，企图引项少龙入伏。项少龙识破诡计，反将池子春制服并逼问出幕后主使为仲孙龙。他随后潜入柴房，纵火烧敌，重伤沙立。凤菲得知沙立被擒后将叛徒逐出歌舞姬团。夜间凤菲与项少龙长谈，心灰意冷欲隐退，项少龙承诺助其脱身并以真实身份晋见齐王。翌日仲孙玄华前来求情，项少龙顺水人情交还沙立。吕不韦亲自来访，试图拉拢项少龙，项少龙断然拒绝并警觉其阴谋——吕不韦可能以小盘身世为撒手锏。凤菲与项少龙商议后续安排，歌舞姬团危机暂时化解。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "池子春",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小人又有要事须向管事报告。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "池子春",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不如借一步到园内说话，那就不虞给人看见。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "text": "这么晚了！谁会看到我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "池子春",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "其实我是想领管事到园里看一对狗男女幽会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "text": "是二小姐吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "池子春",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "还有沙立，若非我一直留意谷明等人，仍不知他们安排沙立偷进来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "text": "带路！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "text": "人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "池子春",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "就在柴房里，我们要小心点，谷明等会在附近给他们把风，管事随小人来吧！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "池子春",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "管事快来！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "text": "我尚有一事未弄清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "池子春",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "text": "那是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "text": "还想骗我，二小姐仍在她的闺房里，我亲眼看到的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "池子春",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈爷饶命，小人不知道二小姐返回房间了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "text": "谁在那里伏击我？只要你敢说不知道，我立即割开你少许咽喉，任你淌血致死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "池子春",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈爷饶命，是沙立逼我这么做的。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "text": "仲孙龙派了多少人来助沙立？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chi_zi_chun",
      "speaker_name": "池子春",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "原来沈爷什么都知道，小人知罪了。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_li",
      "speaker_name": "沙立",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "池子春那狗奴才怎办事的，和那狗杂种躲在那里干什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_li",
      "speaker_name": "沙立",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要杀我！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "沈管事不是病得爬不起来吗？为何转眼又和解子元溜了出去鬼混，更大发神威，擒凶惩恶？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "刚才我见到你的情郎。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "由今晚开始，凤菲再没有情郎，以后都不会有。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "不是这么严重吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你不明白的。我曾向他提及仲孙龙的事，请他凭仲孙玄华师兄弟的身份说几句话，却给他一口回绝，并明言不会私下去见仲孙玄华。唉！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "凤菲现在心灰意冷，只想找个隐僻之地，静静度过下半生。什么风光，都一概与我无关。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "这正是本人的梦想，我对战争和仇杀，早深切厌倦。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "终于肯说出真心话吗？凤菲早知你是这样的人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "什么人也好，假设大小姐肯答应让二小姐做接班人，我可保证助大小姐完成你的梦想。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你凭什么可保证能办得到呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "'项少龙'三个字足够吗？",
      "tone": "自信",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这不是真的！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "若不是我，今天大小姐来探病，小弟怎会见毒指环而色变，逼着将韩竭见仲孙玄华的事说出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "凤菲那样对你，为何你仍肯帮人家呢？",
      "tone": "感激",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "大小姐本身绝非坏人，只是惯了与对大小姐有狼子野心的人周旋，故不敢轻易信人吧！",
      "tone": "理解",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家现在该怎办才好？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "吕不韦今晚已认出沈良是项少龙，我再隐瞒身份对自己有害无益，明天我索性以项少龙的身份晋见齐王，那时谁想动你，均需考虑后果。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你不怕给人加害吗？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_feng_fei",
      "text": "若我在这里有什么事，齐人岂能免祸。我已厌倦左遮右瞒的生活，现在归心似箭，只想尽早回家与妻儿相聚。大小姐若要在秦国找个安居的地方，我保证可给你办到。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "凤菲",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "凤菲的心早死了，一切听从上将军的安排。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小弟有一不情之请，万望沈兄给我仲孙家一点面子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "仲孙兄既有这番话，我沈良怎敢计较，沙立交回仲孙兄，其他话都不必说了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "speaker_name": "仲孙玄华",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我交了沈兄这位朋友。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "小弟一直当仲孙兄是朋友。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fei_chun",
      "speaker_name": "费淳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "秦国的仲父吕不韦爷来找管事！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhong_sun_xuan_hua",
      "text": "仲孙兄该猜到沈良是小弟的假名字！迟点和仲孙兄详谈。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙真厉害，竟可化身沈良，躲到临淄来。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lu_bu_wei",
      "text": "仲父怕是非常失望吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙何出此言？储君不知多么担心你的安危，现在老夫遇上少龙，自会全力保护少龙返回咸阳，今天来只是看少龙的意向为何？",
      "tone": "诚恳",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lu_bu_wei",
      "text": "此事迟一步再说，现在我再没有隐瞒身份的必要，故请仲父正式向齐王提出本人在此的事，好让我以本来身份向他晋见。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "为何我们间的关系会弄至如此田地？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lu_bu_wei",
      "text": "似乎不该由末将负责吧？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是我错了，只不知事情是否仍有挽回的地步。只要我们同心合力辅助政储君，天下将是我大秦囊中之物。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_lu_bu_wei",
      "text": "由始至终，我项少龙是爱好和平的人，只是被迫应战。我们之间的事已非只凭空口白话可以解决的了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_bu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "吕不韦",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "本仲父绝不会怪少龙这么想，当日本仲父想把娘蓉许配少龙，正是表示想修好的诚意。只因刁蛮女儿不听话，才使事情告吹。",
      "tone": "诚恳",
      "chapter": 265,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_bu_wei",
